      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIDING SOLO (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 11 times for five wins and three minors. Was out of the placings last time (30.60) at this track in a OPEN, finishing eighth and beaten 7 lengths. Looks well placed and should feature. WYNDRA ALL SMOKE (2) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led for much of the way before being grabbed late, finishing a one length second at this track over 510m in 30.15. Leading chance. ZIPPING KRAVITZ (6) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (30.06) last time out at Q Parklands. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Expecting another good run. BREAKOUT LAD (8) won as punters' elect last time – cannot be taken lightly.",
